@startuml
title 网络到 UART 时序图
!include _theme.iuml

actor "PC / GCS" as Client
participant "network_app" as Net
participant "mavlink_bridge" as Bridge
participant "UART Port" as UART
participant "Flight Controller" as FC

Client -> Net : 发送 UDP / TCP 数据
Net -> Bridge : 网络接收回调
Bridge -> Bridge : 判断帧与转发目标
Bridge -> UART : 写入串口
UART -> FC : 输出到飞控
@enduml
